Package: tqr
Type: Package
Title: Add tq_xx functions to tidyquant package to facilitate economic analyses
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Mitsuo Shiota
Maintainer: Mitsuo Shiota <mitsuo.shiota.xv@hitachi.com>
Description: Utility functions to facilitate economic analyses on
    time series data in tidy dataframe, which is advocated by tidyquant
    package, and is consisted of three columns named date, symbol and price.
    Functions are: 
    create tidy dataframe (tq_tidy), insert missing rows (tq_pad), 
    calculate differences (tq_diff), moving averages (tq_ma), 
    growth rates (tq_gr) and seasonally adjusted (tq_sa), and 
    convert to lower frequency (tq_to_freq).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.3)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
